room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Escape Mission Chattanooga in Chattanooga
room_description:
Your team runs a successful crime ring, and today you will face your biggest challenge. Crack the safe at the Mission Bank and Trust. Your Recon team has reported a lucrative, but difficult to compromise vault there.
Phase one is complete: the security cameras and phone systems are offline. They have discreetly left clues, tools, and hints around, which you will use to crack the safe. The systems are down for 60 minutes. Will you open the safe and escape before law enforcement arrives?
